plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: GET ItemRevs With Unreleased JTs
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: Query to find Item Revisions with unreleased JT (DirectModel) datasets attached to it

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM ItemRevision WHERE "items_tag.item_id" = "${item_id = }" AND "item_revision_id" = "${item_revision_id = }" AND "object_type" = "${object_type = }" AND "release_status_list.name" = "${Item Revision Status = }" AND "Dataset:IMAN_Rendering.object_type" = "DirectModel" AND "Dataset:IMAN_Rendering.date_released" IS_NULL "IS_NULL"
